          "name": "the integrated proposal has no design-significant persistence mechanism",
          "accepts": ["no design-significant persistence mechanism", "no persistence mechanism is design-significant", "persistence is not design-significant", "does not require a design-significant persistence mechanism"],
          "rejects": ["requires a design-significant persistence mechanism", "persistence mechanism is design-significant", "MySQL is design-significant", "requires MySQL"]
